title: The Anchor
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Indian, International, Asian, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. All vegan dishes are marked (Ve) and all vegetarian dishes are marked (V). Many vegetarian dishes can be made vegan upon request. Vegan options include: Vietnamese veg curry, veg penang curry, chips, skin-on-fries, made-in-house potato wedges, onion rings, house salad, sauteed mushrooms, corn on the cob, hummus & cumin flatbread, harissa rice, lime & coriander infused rice; roasted vegetable jalfrezi can be made vegan if served with mixed salad and rice instead of the naan bread.
